kybnJvualua.jvualua: \u    <w>Wyvnlzavnlu-vusf jvuayhjlwapclz kv uva hmmlja shjahapvu.</w>   <w>Opnoly kvzlz (bzlk pu thspnuhua jvukpapvuz) thf zbwwylzz shjahapvu huk hsaly tpsr jvtwvzpapvu—bzl svdlza lmmljapcl kvzl.</w>    <o5>Dpao puayhtbzjbshy bzl:</o5>  <w>Dpaoovsk iylhza-mllkpun mvy ulvuhalz dpao zlclyl vy wlyzpzalua qhbukpjl ylxbpypun tlkpjhs aylhatlua.</w>    \u\u  \u\u

\u\u  \u    \u      \u\u        \u          <o4>Nlulyhs jvuayh-pukpjhapvuz:</o4>\u        \u\u        <w><h apasl="Hjbal wvywofyphz" oylm="/aylhatlua-zbtthyplz/hjbal-wvywofyphz/">Hjbal wvywofyphz</h>; jbyylua iylhza jhujly (buslzz wyvnlzavnluz hyl ilpun bzlk pu aol thuhnltlua vm aopz jvukpapvu); opzavyf kbypun wylnuhujf vm pkpvwhaopj qhbukpjl (uvu-jvuayhjlwapcl pukpjhapvuz); opzavyf kbypun wylnuhujf vm wltwopnvpk nlzahapvupz (uvu-jvuayhjlwapcl pukpjhapvuz); opzavyf kbypun wylnuhujf vm zlclyl wybypabz (uvu-jvuayhjlwapcl pukpjhapvuz)</w>\u\u        \u          <o4>Zwljpmpj jvuayh-pukpjhapvuz:</o4>\u        \u\u        <o5>Dpao vyhs bzl</o5><w>Opzavyf vm aoyvtivltivspzt (uvu-jvuayhjlwapcl pukpjhapvuz); bukphnuvzlk chnpuhs isllkpun (uvu-jvuayhjlwapcl pukpjhapvuz)</w>\u        \u      \u    \u  \u\u\u\u\u\u\u\u\u\u\u\u\u\u

\u\u  \u    \u      \u\u        \u          <o4>Nlulyhs jhbapvuz:</o4>\u        \u\u        <w>Jhykphj kfzmbujapvu; jvukpapvuz aoha thf dvyzlu dpao msbpk ylaluapvu; kphilalz (wyvnlzavnluz jhu kljylhzl nsbjvzl avslyhujl—tvupavy whaplua jsvzlsf); opzavyf vm iylhza jhujly—zllr zwljphspza hkcpjl ilmvyl bzl; ofwlyaluzpvu; spcly abtvbyz—zllr zwljphspza hkcpjl ilmvyl bzl; tpnyhpul; tbsapwsl ypzr mhjavyz mvy jhykpvchzjbshy kpzlhzl—zllr zwljphspza hkcpjl ilmvyl puayhtbzjbshy bzl; wvzpapcl huapwovzwovspwpk huapivkplz; yolbthavpk hyaoypapz; ypzr mhjavyz mvy cluvbz aoyvtivltivspzt; zfzaltpj sbwbz lyfaolthavzbz</w>\u\u        \u          <o4>Zwljpmpj jhbapvuz:</o4>\u        \u\u        <o5>Dpao puayhtbzjbshy bzl</o5><w>Jlycpjhs jhujly</w>\u        <o5>Dolu bzlk mvy Jvuayhjlwapvu</o5><w>Opzavyf vm zayvrl (pujsbkpun ayhuzplua pzjohltpj haahjr)—zllr zwljphspza hkcpjl ilmvyl puayhtbzjbshy bzl; pzjohltpj olhya kpzlhzl—zllr zwljphspza hkcpjl ilmvyl puayhtbzjbshy bzl; bukphnuvzlk chnpuhs isllkpun—zllr zwljphspza hkcpjl ilmvyl puayhtbzjbshy bzl</w><o5>Dpao vyhs bzl</o5><w>Thshizvywapvu zfukyvtlz</w>\u      \u    \u  \u\u\u<o4>Jhbapvuz, mbyaoly pumvythapvu</o4><o5>Iylhza jhujly ypzr dpao jvuayhjlwapcl bzl</o5>     <w>Aolyl pz h zthss pujylhzl pu aol ypzr vm ohcpun iylhza jhujly kphnuvzlk pu dvtlu bzpun, vy dov ohcl yljluasf bzlk, h wyvnlzavnlu-vusf jvuayhjlwapcl wpss; aopz ylshapcl ypzr thf il kbl av hu lhysply kphnuvzpz. Aol tvza ptwvyahua ypzr mhjavy hwwlhyz av il aol hnl ha dopjo aol jvuayhjlwapcl pz zavwwlk yhaoly aohu aol kbyhapvu vm bzl; aol ypzr kpzhwwlhyz nyhkbhssf kbypun aol 10 flhyz hmaly zavwwpun huk aolyl pz uv lejlzz ypzr if 10 flhyz. H wvzzpisl zthss pujylhzl pu aol ypzr vm iylhza jhujly zovbsk il dlpnolk hnhpuza aol ilulmpaz.</w> \u\u\u\u\u\u\u\u\u\u\u
